Eat or Yeet 2.0
So i got this idea while watching one of you guys video’s. So basically every one get’s the same dish some are good and maybe 1 or 2 are bad...
It’s very easy there are multiple rounds and everyone contests in those rounds, so that means u eat multiple dishes.

These are the rules but it’s a little different:
1. Everyone plays till the end of the game
2. You eat the dish you get a point and go to the next round
3. You yeet no points... but you also still go to the next
4. The person with the most points wins the game.

So i hope u guys can do something with this and maybe will see it in a video u can adjust it if you want
✌️
